sequenceDiagram
  participant IF as IF Stage
  participant ID as ID Stage
  participant BDU as BDU
  participant HU as Hazard Unit
  participant PCN as PC Next

  IF->>ID: Fetch/decode candidate
  ID->>BDU: Evaluate condition with CC flags
  BDU-->>ID: branch_take + target
  ID->>HU: branch_take_commit
  HU-->>IF: flush_ifid=1
  ID->>PCN: branch_target
  PCN-->>IF: redirected PC
  Note over IF,ID: fall-through is annulled
